sentence: In trading on Wednesday, shares of Home Depot Inc (Symbol: HD) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $130.75, changing hands as high as $133.06 per share.
Home Depot Inc shares are currently trading up about 3.2% on the day.

The chart below shows the one year performance of HD shares, versus its 200 day moving average:

Looking at the chart above, HD's low point in its 52 week range is $109.62 per share, with $139.00 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $132.99.
According to the ETF Finder at ETF Channel, HD makes up 7.31% of the Retail ETF (Symbol: RTH) which is trading higher by about 1.5% on the day Wednesday.
